<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Pizza By The Slice: Order Form</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rock+3D&family=Sedan:ital@0;1&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <h1>ORDER FORM</h1>
    </header>

    <header class="banner">
      <h1>PIZZA by the SLICE</h1>
      <p>The pizza-way to bring people together</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <h2>OUR HISTORY</h2>
        <p>
          PIZZA by the SLICE started as a small dream back in 2000. It was
          founded by three people who just wanted to share their love for good
          pizza. Started in a tiny kitchen with only a single oven and a handful
          of recipes, it has grown into people's favorite spot over the years.
          You’ll still find the same fresh ingredients and the same passion that
          was there on the very first day. Because every pizza is a way to bring
          people together.
        </p>

        <h2 class="contact">CONTACT US</h2>
        <p>
          Feel free to contact us for orders and reservations. <br />
          <strong>Address:</strong> 112 Third Laboratory, WeST City<br />
          <strong>Phone:</strong> +639123456789<br />
          <strong>Email:</strong> bsit2b@bicol-u.edu.ph
        </p>

        <h2 class="owners-heading">THE PIZZA MAKERS</h2>
        <p>
          Jessa Mae Mancera<br />
          Mark Louie Morales<br />
          Lawrence Johnkiel Taronga
        </p>
      </aside>

      <main class="content">
        <form>
          <h2>PERSONAL DETAILS</h2>
          <label for="fullname">Full Name:</label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="fullname"
            name="fullname"
            required
            minlength="5"
            maxlength="60"
          /><br />

          <label for="email">Email:</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required /><br />

          <label for="phone">Phone Number:</label>
          <input
            type="tel"
            id="phone"
            name="phone"
            required
            pattern="[0-9]{7,11}"
          /><br />

          <label for="age">Age:</label>
          <input
            type="number"
            id="age"
            name="age"
            required
            min="13"
            max="99"
          /><br />

          <h2>PIZZA SIZE</h2>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input type="radio" id="small" name="pizza_size" value="small" />
            <label for="small">Small</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input
              type="radio"
              id="medium"
              name="pizza_size"
              value="medium"
              checked
            />
            <label for="medium">Medium</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input type="radio" id="large" name="pizza_size" value="large" />
            <label for="large">Large</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input
              type="radio"
              id="extralarge"
              name="pizza_size"
              value="extralarge"
            />
            <label for="extralarge">Extra Large</label>
          </div>

          <h2>CRUST TYPE</h2>
          <select id="crust" name="crust" required>
            <option value="" disabled selected>-- Choose a crust --</option>
            <option value="thin">Thin</option>
            <option value="thick">Thick</option>
            <option value="stuffed">Stuffed</option>
            <option value="gluten-free">Gluten-Free</option></select
          ><br />

          <h2>PIZZA SAUCE</h2>
          <select id="sauce" name="sauce" required>
            <optgroup label="Classic">
              <option value="tomato">Tomato</option>
              <option value="garlic-white">Garlic White</option>
            </optgroup>
            <optgroup label="Special">
              <option value="pesto">Pesto</option>
              <option value="barbecue">Barbecue</option>
            </optgroup></select
          ><br />

          <h2>PIZZA TOPPINGS</h2>

          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input
              type="checkbox"
              id="cheese"
              name="topping"
              value="cheese"
              checked
              disabled
            />
            <label for="cheese">Cheese (Always Included)</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input
              type="checkbox"
              id="pepperoni"
              name="topping"
              value="pepperoni"
            />
            <label for="pepperoni">Pepperoni</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input
              type="checkbox"
              id="mushrooms"
              name="topping"
              value="mushrooms"
            />
            <label for="mushrooms">Mushrooms</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input type="checkbox" id="onions" name="topping" value="onions" />
            <label for="onions">Onions</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input
              type="checkbox"
              id="bellpepper"
              name="topping"
              value="bellpepper"
            />
            <label for="bellpepper">Bell Pepper</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input type="checkbox" id="olives" name="topping" value="olives" />
            <label for="olives">Olives</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input type="checkbox" id="bacon" name="topping" value="bacon" />
            <label for="bacon">Bacon</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input
              type="checkbox"
              id="pineapple"
              name="topping"
              value="pineapple"
              title="Warning: Pineapple on pizza is controversial!"
            />
            <label for="pineapple">Pineapple</label>
          </div>

          <h2>DELIVERY METHOD</h2>

          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input
              type="radio"
              id="delivery"
              name="deliverymethod"
              value="homedelivery"
            />
            <label for="delivery">Home Delivery</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check-item">
            <input
              type="radio"
              id="pickup"
              name="deliverymethod"
              value="storepick-up"
            />
            <label for="pickup">Store Pick-up</label> <br />
            <br />
          </div>

          <label for="address">Delivery Address:</label>
          <textarea
            id="address"
            name="address"
            rows="4"
            placeholder="Enter your delivery address here..."
          ></textarea
          ><br />

          <h2>PAYMENT INFORMATION</h2>

          <fieldset>
            <legend>Payment Details</legend>

            <label for="paymentmethod">Payment Method:</label><br />
            <select id="paymentmethod" name="paymentmethod" required>
              <option value="">--Select Payment Method--</option>
              <option value="creditcard">Credit Card</option>
              <option value="gcash">GCash</option>
              <option value="cashondelivery">Cash on Delivery</option></select
            ><br /><br />

            <label for="cardnumber">
              Card Number (Required for Credit Card only): </label
            ><br />
            <input
              type="text"
              id="cardnumber"
              name="cardnumber"
              pattern="[0-9]{16}"
              placeholder="1234567890123456"
              title="Please enter exactly 16 digits (numbers only, no spaces)"
            /><br />
          </fieldset>

          <br />

          <h2>ORDER SUMMARY</h2>

          <table border="1" cellpadding="8">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Size</th>
                <th>Base Price</th>
                <th>Extra Toppings (each)</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Small</td>
                <td>₱199</td>
                <td>+₱20</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Medium</td>
                <td>₱299</td>
                <td>+₱25</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Large</td>
                <td>₱399</td>
                <td>+₱30</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Extra Large</td>
                <td>₱499</td>
                <td>+₱35</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <br /><br />

          <div class="form-buttons">
            <button type="submit">Place My Order</button>
            <button type="reset">Start Over</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
